               <msContents>
                  <summary>Antiphonary for the Fast of Lent, ጾመ፡ ድጓ፡, owned by <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3504Demetros"> Dǝmeṭros Gäbrä Maryam </persName></summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="91v" facs="005">Fols 1r–91v</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3178Deggwa">Dǝggʷā</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ንዌጥን፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ጽሒፈ፡ ጾመ ድጓ፡ በመሐትወ፡ ድራር፡ ጾም፡ በ፪ ሃሌ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ዘወረደ፡ እምላዕሉ፡ አይሁድ፡ ሰቀሉ፡ ወሚመ፡ ኢያእመሩ፡ እግዚአ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዘየሐዩ፡ በቃሉ፡</incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>(incorrectly labeled Book of the Sabbath of the Faith [Sänbätä Amin] on the inside cover)</note>
                  <notatedMusic><desc>with musical notation</desc></notatedMusic>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="92r" to="93r" facs="096">Fols 92r–93r</locus><title>Halleluiatic chants</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
