                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a1">
                    <locus target="#93r" facs="097">Fol. 93r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    in blue ink: “I, Nǝburä ‘Ǝdǝ Dǝmeṭǝros (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ንቡረ፡ እድ፡ ድሜጥሮስ፡ ገብረ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign> [director of the EOTC and founder of Maḥǝbärä Ḥawarǝyat in Eretria]), commissioned this manuscript of Ṣomä Dǝggwa with my own money; it is to be kept in the library which I built.”
                    mentions <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3504Demetros"> Dǝmeṭros Gäbrä Maryam </persName>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
